title: Black Coffin Transcendent - Novel Updates
genre: Adventure   Fantasy   Harem   School Life   Shounen
author: 浅木夢見道
description:
Shinya is a high-ranked Aublade, one of thirteen in the entire world.

That is, until he dies.

Shinya’s alternate reality self gets awakened in his body to find himself being attacked by an insect monster.

How will he live in his new existence.. assuming he can beat all of the monsters who are attacking him?!?
>
